    "body": "Package rlp prevents nil pointers during decoding. You can make it work by adding the \"nil\" struct tag:\r\n\r\n```text\r\ntype B struct {\r\n\tAPoint *A     `rlp:\"nil\"`\r\n\tB1     string\r\n}\r\n```",
